    "These proxy human agents are behavior cloning agents trained using human data by Carroll et al. (2019b).",
    "As shown in Table 4, we discover that LLM agents outperform both Behavior Cloning as well as PPO agents trained with human data.",
    "Apart from the Asymmetric Advantages layout, they also match or outperform the Hidden Utility Self-play (HSP) baseline, which is designed to excel at ZSC.In Hanabi, we pair our agents with Off-Belief Learning (OBL) agents (Hu et al., 2021a).",
    "OBL is a MARL strategy that generates grounded clues and actions and is the state-of-the-art method for crossplay in Hanabi.",
    "OBL agents provide observationgrounded clues and collaborate well with humans."
